CrudRepository methods
========================
save(S entity)								: Save or update an entity.

saveAll(Iterable<S> entities)				: Save or update multiple entities.

findById(ID id)								: Find an entity by its ID.

existsById(ID id)							: Check if an entity with a given ID exists.

findAll()									: Get all entities.

findAllById(Iterable<ID> ids)				: Get a list of entities by their IDs.

count()										: Get the number of entities.

deleteById(ID id)							: Delete an entity by its ID.

delete(T entity)							: Delete a specific entity.

deleteAll(Iterable<? extends T> entities)	: Delete multiple entities.

deleteAll()									: Delete all entities.

